{"tid":2442051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"正義姐疑踩場遭私了 聽障男生今受審 藍雪寶：我驚我會死 因為我有心臟病","createTime":"2021-03-11T06:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T10:03:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a099bf778a5e18827fd90fd678cd8252dda633ee","tid":2442051,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"有「正義姐」之稱的教師藍雪寶與同伴帶國旗踩場抗議，與示威者爭執，最終藍雪寶遭「私了」。一名聽障男生被指多次用手機毆打藍的頭部，而與藍同行的女商人宋晞綸則涉推撞在場人士並以國旗施襲。男生與宋晞綸分別被控傷人及打鬥罪，由於男被告是聽障人士，早前案件開審時聽取證供有困難 ，裁判官將案件押後至今天，讓法庭安排傳譯員及即時字幕顯示聆訊內容設施。藍雪寶今作供憶述遇襲經過時揚言：「我驚我會死。」<br />\n<br />\n首名證人藍雪寶透露自己亦有聽障，甫出庭即向法庭申請助聽器。裁判官鄧少雄宣佈休庭稍作安排。審訊以英語進行，蔡和藍戴上助聽器，由傳譯員將聆訊內容翻譯成廣東話。操普通話的宋晞綸則由另一名傳譯員將聆訊內容翻譯成普通話。聆訊開始及結束時，鄧官均向蔡確認他清楚明白審訊內容。<br />\n<br />\n藍供稱，當日下午近1時，她到宋位於銅鑼灣的辦公室，準備參加一個到九龍區派免費口罩的義工活動。她從辦公室窗外看到時代廣場空地放有黑底白字的布匹，上面寫有光時口號。當控方問到有關口號時，藍即詢問法庭：「我係咪可以講個句嘢出嚟？」鄧官謂：「你畀緊口供，可以講你見到同聽到嘅。」藍則稱：「我睇到寫上『光復香港 時代革命』。」<br />\n<br />\n未幾她下樓行至時代廣場外，打算前往會合宋的司機，準備離開銅鑼灣，其間她看見一名身穿短袖黑衫的青年主動走向宋，並以粗口罵宋。藍見狀上前用手機錄影，拍到該青年踢向宋，使宋退後，其間她突然被另一名身穿黑色連帽外套男子搶去手機。該男子隨即轉身離去，她連忙拉扯其背包，欲取回手機。<br />\n<br />\n藍續指，宋走到她身邊時，遭一班人圍毆。一名短袖黑衣青年用右手箍她，又用膝撞肚並將她摔倒地上。她又供稱宋同樣被人打至跌倒，並有人壓在宋身上，及後被拉扯出去繼續打。她一度緊張謂：「我當時好痛，亦都流緊血，我好驚，我驚我會死，因為我有心臟病。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/5KP4YGPJOZAGBPBBFBXHNMAAUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2F5KP4YGPJOZAGBPBBFBXHNMAAUA%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=6734b2c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2F5KP4YGPJOZAGBPBBFBXHNMAAUA%2F&h=aaf52439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/5KP4YGPJOZAGBPBBFBXHNMAAUA/</a>"},{"pid":"3c75ad993714921180a18f90bb7a86afc438cac4","tid":2442051,"uid":93986,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:28:00.000Z","msg":"死撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"04c2b0aa8c5976244051485216b59e7d113fa295","tid":2442051,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1b1e04ecc51aaa64ce30eb4d56958012aa3dc0","tid":2442051,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"邊個藍雪寶？"},{"pid":"bae89958738571b70fffef6b8a5824433796c3d9","tid":2442051,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:37:11.000Z","msg":"次次拎重武器殺得死人嘅係狗同藍絲，鬧人打人殺人冇後果嘅又係狗同藍絲，然後次次都係狗同藍絲講話驚自己就嚟死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9147c84fc25fd30819bf62284ac1c541cff210","tid":2442051,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"唔去果度咪無事"},{"pid":"2b33fcbd007affd5ee8a399fff839b1ffccabebf","tid":2442051,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:40:29.000Z","msg":"唔死真係冇天理"},{"pid":"73cb7a8eb01fb6cd6ef68e9081075dc20b9b1998","tid":2442051,"uid":23832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"仆街手痕google一吓<br />\n屌你老母成個支那閪咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死返上去啦支那寶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYw7rKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYw7rKL.jpg&h=d0490209&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLWSCRq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLWSCRq.jpg&h=f9a9b6af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c4fe69ce551cde0edabf0e0bcfe576c36d2a7e7","tid":2442051,"uid":373783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:49:26.000Z","msg":"快撚啲死喇垃圾. DLLM"},{"pid":"0886dcba23d4673e8c571b26ae6d028a45a4e0fc","tid":2442051,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"撩交打之後話怕死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc54d5f487747f04d7df30d8b271f631193b1d4","tid":2442051,"uid":57674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73cb7a8eb01fb6cd6ef68e9081075dc20b9b1998","tid":2442051,"uid":23832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"仆街手痕google一吓<br />\n屌你老母成個支那閪咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死返上去啦支那寶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYw7rKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYw7rKL.jpg&h=d0490209&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLWSCRq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLWSCRq.jpg&h=f9a9b6af&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:52:17.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲樣真係一岩一忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪細個俾老豆老母生到咁撚樣之後<br />\n心理唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536963c5901b2d530c1dd8b111815febf46003ce","tid":2442051,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"藍指稱，她被另一名穿著黑色短袖 T 恤的男子箍著，該男以膝蓋撞擊藍的腹部，並將她「撻落地」，被多人毆打的宋則跌倒壓在其身上。裁判官問及藍，該男子如何將她「撻落地」及男子的手部接觸到她的何處時，藍回應指「我睇唔到，我淨係感覺到我畀人掟落地」。藍補充，她當時在流血，情況混亂，重申「我好驚，我驚我會死，因為我有心臟病」，但肯定該男子的手部與她的身體有接觸。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0-lunch-%E6%89%93%E9%AC%A5%E6%A1%88%E5%85%A9%E8%A2%A